<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>mn mtẖlk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ʿnd ktẖrẗ ạlhmwm tʿzyạtk tldẖdẖ nfsy

[V2]
 ḥyn tw̉lmny ạltjạrb ậrạk ạ̉nt ʿzy wtrsy

[V3]
 tsẖrq brwḥk dạkẖly ftgẖyr ạlạ̉ḥwạl

[V4]
 lạ sẖyʾ ʿlyk ystḥyl wlạ ạ̉mrạaⁿ mḥạl

[V5]
 ạlqrạr - mn mtẖlk yạ sydy fy qdrtk fy qwtk

[V6]
 ʿjybẗ hy ạ̉ʿmạlk wllmwt mḥbtk

[V7]
 tkẖrj mn ạlậkl ạ̉klạaⁿ wḥlạwẗ mn ạljạfy

[V8]
 tftḥ fy ạlṣkẖr drbạ tlms jrḥạ wtʿạfy

[V9]
 2- tfyḍ ʿly̱ ạlmsạkyn bnʿm kẖyrạtk

[V10]
 tftḥ llbạỷsyn ạ̉bwạbạaⁿ fy smwạtk

[V11]
 lsẖkẖṣk hyạ̉t sbḥạaⁿ mn ạ̉fwạh ạlrḍʿạn

[V12]
 fy rwḥk mly̱ʾ ạlḥyạẗ wlạ yḥdk zmạn</lyrics>
